{
  "stem": "10496.4",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And so, as you can see, the sculpture, it's like flames.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Notice the flames?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it's very emotional for me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It means [NON-ENGLISH], which means 'thou shall not kill.' And it's been-- it's been really great to have this.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It's wonderful.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It reminds me--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Absolutely, yes, yes.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Completely.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This is important.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, well this is the concentration camp in Gurs, and this is the main street here.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it looks like a, a truck or something on there, but notice the barracks.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And this is what Gurs looked like.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And Gurs, as you know, was divided up into sections called [NON-ENGLISH]",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, the first camp.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, it's a group picture of some of the workers that, that were on the labor farm.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "After my father came back from, from Dachau, of course, he lost his job, you know?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So he worked in the labor-- on the labor farm.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And these are some of the-- in fact, you see a picture of me in there because I visited them.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, it had to be around '39, 1939.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's a picture of the Les Milles camp.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It's a big, big building.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That's all it is.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "A lot of people in there but it's not like the Gurs camp where they have barracks.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, it had to be taken in 19-- 1941, somewhere in 1941.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We're watching a soccer game.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And notice, by the way, nobody was worried about what's going to happen in the future.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Nobody knew at that time that-- what the Germans were going to do to us.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So you can see, that we still think we're just a bunch of prisoners.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "1940. '41, '41, Yeah.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, when I was at Quaker home for three months or so, these are some of the people that befriended me or I became friends with them.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And these are some of the kids that we're in that-- all Spanish.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Civil war, right, Spanish Civil War.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, my daughter Linda and she's holding Laura, her niece.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then next to her is Erin, that's her daughter.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then Scott, as you know, he's very tall.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, and then my wife and then myself.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then my daughter-in-law with Diana.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Diana at that time was young, very, very little.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then my son Stephen.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that's my family, and I hope it will grow.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
